Embed & analyze:
>> python cli.py --embed --input 1.pgm --output s1.png --text "secret message" --payload 0.5 --analyze

Detect in image:
>> python cli.py --image s1.png

Extract from image:
>> python cli.py --extract s1.png

Recursive convert pgm to png
>> python convert_pgm_dataset.py --input bossbase --output bossbase_png